{"pageProps":{"post":{"mdxSource":"<img src=\"https://cdn.ipfsscan.io/weibo/large/005ZoLfCgy1ht1c97a6m0j30ws0e6gr0.jpg\" />\n\n<h2>godot中新的音乐资源</h2>\n<p>新资源 AudioStreamInteractive、AudioStreamPlaylist 和 AudioStreamSynchronized 使您能够创建复杂的分层音乐和过渡。</p>\n<p>这样，你就可以构建自己的动态音乐系统，让它对游戏的上下文做出反应。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>AudioStreamInteractive：允许将多个剪辑设置为子流，并编辑它们之间的过渡表。</li>\n<li>AudioStreamPlaylist：允许按顺序或随机播放流列表。</li>\n<li>AudioStreamSynchronized：允许同步播放多个流，可以控制每个流的音量。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>这三种流类型可以组合起来，创建复杂、分层的互动音乐以及它们之间的过渡，类似于 WWise、FMOD 或 Elias 等软件。</p>\n<p>例如：</p>\n<p>AudioStreamInteractive 的 AudioStreamPlaylist 版本类似于 WWise 处理交互式音乐的方式。\nAudioStreamInteractive 中的 AudioStreamSynchronized 类似于 Elias 处理互动音乐的方式。</p>\n<p>在 Godot 风格中，这些组件是独立呈现的，用户可以混合和匹配以实现所需的功能。</p>\n","frontMatter":{"readingTime":{"text":"2 min read","minutes":1.245,"time":74700,"words":249},"slug":"godot-release/4.3/godot4.3-新的音乐资源节点","fileName":"godot-release/4.3/godot4.3-新的音乐资源节点.md","date":"2024-08-26T00:00:00.000Z","tags":["godot"],"category":["godot-release"],"thumbnail":"https://cdn.ipfsscan.io/weibo/large/005ZoLfCgy1ht1c97a6m0j30ws0e6gr0.jpg","draft":false,"keywords":["godot教程","godot中文教程","godot开发教程","godot更新日志"],"title":"godot4.3-新的音乐资源节点"}},"prev":{"date":"2024-08-26T00:00:00.000Z","tags":["godot"],"category":["godot-release"],"thumbnail":"https://cdn.ipfsscan.io/weibo/large/005ZoLfCgy1ht1cdcfv7ej30wq0e276k.jpg","draft":false,"keywords":["godot教程","godot中文教程","godot开发教程","godot更新日志"],"title":"web导出的单线程模式","slug":"godot-release/4.3/web导出的单线程模式"},"next":{"date":"2024-08-26T00:00:00.000Z","tags":["godot"],"category":["godot-release"],"thumbnail":"https://cdn.ipfsscan.io/weibo/large/005ZoLfCgy1ht1cckhaskj30wu0e6gtm.jpg","draft":false,"keywords":["godot教程","godot中文教程","godot开发教程","godot更新日志"],"title":"godot4.3-新增tilemap-layer节点","slug":"godot-release/4.3/godot4.3-新增tilemap-layer节点"}},"__N_SSG":true}